<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <h1 style="color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5; padding-bottom: 10px;">Email Change Request Submitted</h1>
      
      <p>Hello <%= @user.first_name.presence || 'there' %>,</p>
      
      <p>We have received your request to change your email address. Here are the details:</p>
      
      <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Current Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Requested New Email:</strong> <%= @email_change_request.new_email %></p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Request Date:</strong> <%= @email_change_request.requested_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @email_change_request.reason %></p>
      </div>
      
      <h2 style="color: #333; font-size: 18px;">What happens next?</h2>
      
      <ul style="line-height: 1.6;">
        <li>Your request will be reviewed by an administrator</li>
        <li>You will receive an email notification once a decision is made</li>
        <li>If approved, your new email will become active immediately</li>
        <li>You will need to use your new email to sign in</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div style="background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e;"><strong>Important:</strong> This request will expire in 30 days if not processed.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>You can view the status of your request at any time by visiting your account settings.</p>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
          This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.<br>
          If you did not request this change, please contact support immediately.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>